  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK722">
<l>kaṟṟāruṭ kaṟṟā reṉappaṭuvar kaṟṟārmuṟ</l>
<l>kaṟṟa celaccollu vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who can agreeably set forth their acquirements before the learned will be regarded as the most learned among the learned.</l>
            </lg>
